Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.88,0:00:02.88,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(veu Shinichi) "Hem anat a passar\Nun cap de setmana
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.96,0:00:04.76,Yellow,,0,0,0,,a la mansió d'un amic\Ndel doctor Agasa."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.84,0:00:09.12,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Només d'arribar-hi, ens hem trobat\Nun home ferit, en Yuji Isehara."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.52,0:00:13.12,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"En Yugi és un 'hacker' professional\Nque feia d'esbirro
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.20,0:00:16.04,Yellow,,0,0,0,,d'un lladre molt violent\Nanomenat el Zorro."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.56,0:00:20.56,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"He pogut salvar en Uigi Sehara\Na l'últim moment
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.64,0:00:22.88,Yellow,,0,0,0,,abans que la banda del Zorro l'assassinés per haver-los traït."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.96,0:00:25.00,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Però ens han seguit, i..."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.68,0:00:33.36,White,,0,0,0,,-Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.68,0:00:33.36,White,,0,0,0,,-Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.96,0:00:37.52,White,,0,0,0,,-Què? En Conan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.96,0:00:37.52,White,,0,0,0,,-Oh... Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.68,0:00:39.72,White,,0,0,0,,-Oh...!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.68,0:00:39.72,White,,0,0,0,,-Oh, Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.64,0:00:42.44,White,,0,0,0,,(Ayumi) Oh...!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.08,0:00:56.68,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Adeu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.32,0:01:00.32,White,,0,0,0,,Oh..., aaaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.72,0:01:02.72,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ah..., mhm!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.96,0:01:04.96,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Mhm...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.24,0:01:08.04,White,,0,0,0,,(tots dos) Aaaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.60,0:01:11.40,White,,0,0,0,,-Aaaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.60,0:01:11.40,White,,0,0,0,,-Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.64,0:01:13.44,White,,0,0,0,,Aaaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.92,0:01:18.96,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"S'aixeca el teló\Ni apareix el protagonista."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.04,0:01:21.68,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Resol els misteris fent\Nuna dansa preciosa."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.76,0:01:23.76,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"El Zorro és un lladre incendiari."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.84,0:01:25.60,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Pels pèls,\Nperò l'acabarem arrissant."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.68,0:01:27.48,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"La veritat sempre s'acaba sabent."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.56,0:01:30.92,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Sembla un nen, però té el cervell d'un adult i és el detectiu Conan!"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.20,0:01:38.16,Songs,,0,0,0,,Amai uso nara tsuiteite.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.96,0:01:46.08,Songs,,0,0,0,,Shinjitsu wa setsunaku itai mono DA-KA-RA Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.52,0:01:48.40,Songs,,0,0,0,,Lie, lie, lie, lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.48,0:01:50.12,Songs,,0,0,0,,Aimai, my, mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.32,0:01:53.28,Songs,,0,0,0,,Isso kimi no subete wo kakete
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.60,0:01:58.48,Songs,,0,0,0,,logical na watashi\Nwo damashi nuite.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.64,0:02:09.00,Songs,,0,0,0,,Kitto hajime wa mujaki na koi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.36,0:02:12.80,Songs,,0,0,0,,eforume shite mita dake soushite.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.16,0:02:16.56,Songs,,0,0,0,,Hikari wo matoi yami ni obieru
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.96,0:02:19.24,Songs,,0,0,0,,ginmaku sutaa no you ni.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.92,0:02:27.24,Songs,,0,0,0,,Sou yo kono mama kyokou no sekai de
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.84,0:02:34.16,Songs,,0,0,0,,nazo wo tokeba oikakeru\Nriyuu ga nakunaru wa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.44,0:02:43.12,Songs,,0,0,0,,Nani mo kamo omoidoori\Nnante tsumaranai!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.88,0:02:47.48,Songs,,0,0,0,,Lie, lie, lie, lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.80,0:02:49.56,Songs,,0,0,0,,Why? Why? Why? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.64,0:02:53.16,Songs,,0,0,0,,Itsuwari demo kamawanai.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.24,0:02:59.84,Songs,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.96,0:03:05.08,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"En Conan cau per un penya-segat\N(segona part)."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.80,0:03:22.80,White,,0,0,0,,Oh! Hola, Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.80,0:03:22.80,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Nois!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.44,0:03:27.32,White,,0,0,0,,En Conan...., en Conan...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.24,0:03:30.48,White,,0,0,0,,No pot ser. No pot ser\Nde cap manera!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.56,0:03:33.28,White,,0,0,0,,Però ho hem vist,\Nels ulls no enganyen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.36,0:03:35.80,White,,0,0,0,,Hem vist perfectament\Ncom en Conan...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.56,0:03:39.20,White,,0,0,0,,queia daltabaix\Nd'aquell penya-segat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.72,0:03:41.52,White,,0,0,0,,(tots dos) Aaaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.44,0:03:46.48,White,,0,0,0,,Sí que ho hem vist...\NHa passat davant nostre.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.56,0:03:49.84,White,,0,0,0,,Tots hem vist\Ncom en Conan queia pel penya-segat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.92,0:03:51.72,White,,0,0,0,,No..., no!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.84,0:03:53.84,White,,0,0,0,,Ahú, ahú...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.84,0:03:53.84,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Pobre Conan...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.64,0:03:56.64,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Per què? Per què...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.16,0:03:59.44,White,,0,0,0,,Em pot explicar què ha passat,\Ninspector?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.52,0:04:03.52,White,,0,0,0,,Què? El Zorro?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.52,0:04:03.52,Green,,0,0,0,,Ha sigut tot cosa del Zorro.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.48,0:04:06.48,White,,0,0,0,,Pel que ens han explicat els nens,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.56,0:04:09.24,White,,0,0,0,,hem deduït que l'home que ha caigut amb en Conan pel penya-segat
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.32,0:04:11.12,White,,0,0,0,,era en Yuji Isehara.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.20,0:04:14.12,White,,0,0,0,,I després de la caiguda, el Zorro\Ni els seus homes han desaparegut.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.20,0:04:16.48,White,,0,0,0,,Fins ara hem sigut incapaços\Nde localitzar-los.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.20,0:04:19.52,Green,,0,0,0,,Suposem que se les han tingut\Nentre ells
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.60,0:04:22.92,Green,,0,0,0,,i que en Conan, d'alguna manera,\Ns'hi ha ficat pel mig.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.00,0:04:26.56,White,,0,0,0,,Em costa d'entendre què hi feia, aquell marrec, amb en Yuji Isehara.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.64,0:04:29.64,Green,,0,0,0,,No ho sé, no en tinc ni idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.64,0:04:29.64,White,,0,0,0,,M'ho pot explicar?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.72,0:04:32.84,Green,,0,0,0,,Demà a primera hora demanarem\Na la policia de Kanagawa
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.92,0:04:34.92,Green,,0,0,0,,que activi el dispositiu de recerca per buscar...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.00,0:04:38.72,White,,0,0,0,,Faci-ho ara mateix! Digui'ls-hi\Nque comencin a buscar-lo ara mateix!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.28,0:04:42.56,White,,0,0,0,,(tots dos) D'acord.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.28,0:04:42.56,Green,,0,0,0,,Ah..., sí, sí, esclar. Vinga!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.28,0:04:47.40,White,,0,0,0,,Punyeta! Com pot ser?! Oh...!\NCom pot haver passat?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.56,0:04:51.36,Cyan,,0,0,0,,(pensa) "Pa... pare..."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.24,0:05:10.24,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Va, tranquils. No patiu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.24,0:05:14.60,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Estic segura que en Conan està bé,\Nja ho veureu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.00,0:05:18.96,White,,0,0,0,,Esclar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.00,0:05:18.96,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Hem de tenir confiança que tornarà.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:21.16,White,,0,0,0,,-I jo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:21.16,White,,0,0,0,,-Jo en tinc.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.80,0:05:23.32,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Bé!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.88,0:05:27.88,White,,0,0,0,,Què, inspector, què se'n sap?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.96,0:05:31.52,Green,,0,0,0,,Fa 3 hores que han activat\Nel dispositiu de recerca,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.60,0:05:34.00,Green,,0,0,0,,però de moment\Nencara no han trobat res.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.44,0:05:36.48,White,,0,0,0,,Oh... Molt bé, gràcies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.76,0:05:41.76,White,,0,0,0,,Pel que ens han dit tots els agents,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.84,0:05:44.08,White,,0,0,0,,allà on van caure l'aigua\Nés molt fonda
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.16,0:05:46.24,White,,0,0,0,,i acostuma a haver-hi corrents\Nmolt forts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.32,0:05:48.72,White,,0,0,0,,El més normal és que el corrent\Nde seguida se'ls hagi emportat
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.80,0:05:50.60,White,,0,0,0,,i els hagi arrossegat mar endins.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.04,0:05:53.72,White,,0,0,0,,També ens han dit\Nque no solen recuperar els cossos.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.80,0:05:55.24,White,,0,0,0,,Què?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.68,0:05:58.52,Green,,0,0,0,,Tot i així, els hem demanat\Nque no aturin la recerca.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.60,0:06:01.16,Green,,0,0,0,,Si se'n sap res,\Nus ho comunicarem de seguida.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.24,0:06:02.96,White,,0,0,0,,D'acord. Mol-moltes gràcies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.32,0:06:05.32,Green,,0,0,0,,La seguretat d'en Conan\Nés important, esclar,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.40,0:06:07.48,Green,,0,0,0,,però segons com trobin\Nen Yuji Isehara,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.56,0:06:09.60,Green,,0,0,0,,el cas del Zorro podria\Nquedar encallat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.68,0:06:12.08,Green,,0,0,0,,I no ho penso permetre\Nde cap manera!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.00,0:06:16.96,White,,0,0,0,,Mm! Gràcies, inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.00,0:06:16.96,Green,,0,0,0,,T'ho ben asseguro.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.08,0:06:28.08,White,,0,0,0,,(Ai, pensa) "Ho vaig veure."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.52,0:06:32.08,White,,0,0,0,,"Vaig veure perfectament...\Ncom queia pel penya-segat."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.60,0:06:39.16,White,,0,0,0,,"Però encara no l'han trobat mort."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.12,0:06:51.20,White,,0,0,0,,"Estic segura que era per aquí."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.56,0:07:24.56,White,,0,0,0,,Soc a dins d'una cova.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.64,0:07:26.64,White,,0,0,0,,-(vent: fiiiu)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.64,0:07:26.64,White,,0,0,0,,-Oh...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.08,0:07:30.08,White,,0,0,0,,Brisa marina.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.80,0:07:32.80,White,,0,0,0,,Això vol dir que més endavant...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.00,0:07:43.80,White,,0,0,0,,Oh! Si no m'equivoco...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.28,0:07:52.00,White,,0,0,0,,Això vol dir que soc just sota\Nel penya-segat per on va caure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.76,0:07:59.40,White,,0,0,0,,Oh! Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.52,0:08:28.56,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Esperi's, no vagi tan de pressa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.24,0:08:31.24,White,,0,0,0,,Vols callar i parar de seguir-me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.32,0:08:34.28,White,,0,0,0,,No puc perdre més temps jugant\Na detectius amb una criatura.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.60,0:08:37.40,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(veu Shinichi) Quines penques:\Nvaig saltar amb ell pel penya-segat,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.48,0:08:39.84,Yellow,,0,0,0,,li vaig salvar la vida,\Ni ni m'ho agraeix ni res.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.24,0:08:42.04,White,,0,0,0,,No, no em mateu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.12,0:08:43.64,White,,0,0,0,,Sisplau!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.16,0:08:46.72,White,,0,0,0,,Després de tots els problemes\Nque ens has portat...,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.80,0:08:48.60,White,,0,0,0,,moriràs com un traïdor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.68,0:08:50.16,White,,0,0,0,,Adeu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.64,0:08:54.44,White,,0,0,0,,Ah..., aaaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.88,0:08:56.60,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ah..., mhm!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.00,0:08:58.80,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Mhm...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.12,0:09:01.92,White,,0,0,0,,(tots dos) Aaaah...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.88,0:09:05.88,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(Shinichi, pensa) "Si som\Njust sobre aquella cova!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.92,0:09:09.52,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"M'he d'arriscar,\Nno tinc cap altra opció."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.80,0:09:11.80,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"He de calcular l'altura\Ndel penya-segat
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.88,0:09:14.32,Yellow,,0,0,0,,i el moment exacte\Nque l'onada topa amb les roques."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.04,0:09:18.48,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Ara!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.40,0:09:22.20,White,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.40,0:09:22.20,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.80,0:09:32.80,White,,0,0,0,,Sí, ja ho sé.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.80,0:09:32.80,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Nedi, nedi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.68,0:09:45.84,White,,0,0,0,,No, esclar que no.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.68,0:09:45.84,Yellow,,0,0,0,,No té intenció d'entregar-se, oi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.92,0:09:48.88,White,,0,0,0,,En conec un que va delatar el Zorro\Ni va fugir a l'estranger,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.96,0:09:51.32,White,,0,0,0,,i al cap d'un temps ell\Nel va localitzar,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.40,0:09:53.96,White,,0,0,0,,el va anar a buscar\Ni el va liquidar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.64,0:09:57.60,White,,0,0,0,,Encara que m'entregués,\Nem trobaria.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.00,0:10:06.64,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Però no pot fugir tota la vida\Ncom si fos un delinqüent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.92,0:10:09.24,White,,0,0,0,,Per això he de rumiar a veure\Ncom m'ho puc fer!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.56,0:10:11.76,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Doncs potser el millor\Nque podria fer
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.84,0:10:14.24,Yellow,,0,0,0,,seria trobar el Zorro\Nabans que el trobi ell a vostè.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.32,0:10:16.76,White,,0,0,0,,Quina bestiesa...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.32,0:10:16.76,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Seria la millor solució.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.52,0:10:19.92,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Però esclar, necessitaria algú\Nque l'ajudés.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.80,0:10:34.80,White,,0,0,0,,(Zorro) Mm... Una exposició amb venda\Nde joies per a nou-rics.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.24,0:10:39.72,White,,0,0,0,,És un cop al mes\Ni cada vegada es fa al mateix lloc.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.92,0:10:42.92,White,,0,0,0,,Quant en trauríem?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.00,0:10:45.04,White,,0,0,0,,Ens estalviaríem d'anar casa per casa
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.12,0:10:47.76,White,,0,0,0,,i amb un sol cop ens enduríem\Nmil milions de iens.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.24,0:10:49.68,White,,0,0,0,,(xiulet d'admiració)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.76,0:10:52.24,White,,0,0,0,,-Com sempre.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.76,0:10:52.24,White,,0,0,0,,-I el tema de la seguretat?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.32,0:10:55.20,White,,0,0,0,,Amb el programa d'en Yuji\Nno tindrem cap problema.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.28,0:10:57.28,White,,0,0,0,,Serà bufar i fer ampolles.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.04,0:11:01.32,White,,0,0,0,,Ha-ha-ha! Parlant d'en Yuji,\Nmira que va ser idiota, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.40,0:11:05.28,White,,0,0,0,,Va ser tan cagacalces, que al final va acabar daltabaix del penya-segat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.36,0:11:09.28,White,,0,0,0,,Això vol dir que ens podrem repartir\Nla seva part, oi que sí, Zorro?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.36,0:11:10.84,White,,0,0,0,,Oh..., oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.16,0:11:17.72,White,,0,0,0,,N'esteu segurs? Si voleu,\Npodem firmar un altre contracte.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.00,0:11:19.80,White,,0,0,0,,He-he-he...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.24,0:11:22.96,White,,0,0,0,,Molt bé, doncs.\NHo farem aquesta nit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.04,0:11:25.04,White,,0,0,0,,Ja ho podeu anar preparant tot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.52,0:11:38.52,White,,0,0,0,,(ocells: piu-piu)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.04,0:11:47.64,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Què? L'Ai també ha desaparegut?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.20,0:11:50.44,White,,0,0,0,,No en tinc ni idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.20,0:11:50.44,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Però, com pot ser?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.52,0:11:52.68,White,,0,0,0,,Jo ni me n'he adonat,\Nque se n'anava.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.76,0:11:55.80,White,,0,0,0,,-La banda del Zorro?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.76,0:11:55.80,White,,0,0,0,,-No pot ser que l'hagin segrestat?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.88,0:11:58.12,White,,0,0,0,,No entenc res,\Nja en començo a estar tip!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.20,0:12:01.72,White,,0,0,0,,Com pot ser que avui tothom faci\Nel que li dona la santa gana?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.08,0:12:04.68,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Ara això no és important, pare.\NFes alguna cosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.76,0:12:07.28,White,,0,0,0,,Sí, ja ho sé! Inspector...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.76,0:12:09.76,White,,0,0,0,,(tots dos) D'acord!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.76,0:12:09.76,Green,,0,0,0,,Aneu a buscar-la.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.84,0:12:13.84,White,,0,0,0,,(ocells: piu-piu)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.92,0:12:35.32,White,,0,0,0,,He vingut sola,\Ntal com m'heu demanat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.72,0:12:45.24,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ai! Em pensava que se m'havia espatllat quan vam caure a l'aigua.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.60,0:12:47.60,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Però t'he pogut enviar el missatge.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.68,0:12:50.52,White,,0,0,0,,No m'hauries d'haver explicat\Nuna altra cosa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.60,0:12:52.04,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.36,0:12:55.76,Yellow,,0,0,0,,És veritat, perdona. Els havia\Nde fer creure que érem morts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.84,0:12:57.92,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Per no posar en perill\Nla seva família.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.20,0:13:04.20,White,,0,0,0,,No... no em matis, sisplau!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.20,0:13:07.60,White,,0,0,0,,T'ho suplico! No em matis!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:12.48,White,,0,0,0,,Per la teva dona i pel teu fill?\NNo siguis tan melodramàtic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:17.44,White,,0,0,0,,Suposo... que has parlat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.56,0:13:23.28,White,,0,0,0,,-Et deixaré triar, doncs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.56,0:13:23.28,White,,0,0,0,,-No, no he dit res!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.44,0:13:27.76,White,,0,0,0,,O em desempallego de la teva dona\Ni del teu fill,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.84,0:13:29.84,White,,0,0,0,,o tu mateix acabes amb la teva vida.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.92,0:13:31.92,White,,0,0,0,,Què t'estimes més?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.88,0:13:35.36,White,,0,0,0,,Tria!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.32,0:13:47.32,White,,0,0,0,,Jo estava molt tranquil·la.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.40,0:13:50.48,White,,0,0,0,,Però no sé com t'ho faràs\Nper explicar-ho als altres.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.76,0:13:53.12,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ah... Ja, tens raó.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.20,0:13:56.20,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ah, per cert, m'has portat\Ntot el que t'he demanat?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.28,0:13:58.28,White,,0,0,0,,Sí, ho tinc aquí.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.44,0:14:05.08,White,,0,0,0,,Ah...! Fantàstic!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.56,0:14:09.68,White,,0,0,0,,Què fa?\NVigili, que és molt delicat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.32,0:14:12.44,White,,0,0,0,,Vaig trigar dos mesos a fer-lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.88,0:14:17.36,White,,0,0,0,,Déu-n'hi-do, quin programa...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.44,0:14:20.04,White,,0,0,0,,Si que són espavilats,\Nels nanos d'avui dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.04,0:14:23.40,White,,0,0,0,,Esclar que jo a la meva època\Nera igual.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.28,0:14:26.28,White,,0,0,0,,Mm... mm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.44,0:14:32.24,White,,0,0,0,,M'ho imaginava.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.32,0:14:35.24,White,,0,0,0,,Han començat a hackejar el sistema\Nde seguretat del seu pròxim objectiu
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.32,0:14:37.36,White,,0,0,0,,fent servir el meu programa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.44,0:14:41.44,White,,0,0,0,,Això vol dir que una d'aquelles dues\Ncontrasenyes era per verificar això.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.52,0:14:43.52,White,,0,0,0,,Però l'altra, per què deu ser?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.12,0:14:48.68,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ara, d'entrada, hauríem d'evitar\Nque el Zorro cometi el delicte.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.76,0:14:50.76,Yellow,,0,0,0,,On tenen pensat atacar?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.36,0:14:54.48,White,,0,0,0,,Aaa... a la Sala d'Exposicions\Ndel barri de Beika.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.04,0:14:57.04,Yellow,,0,0,0,,D'acord.\NHem d'avisar la policia!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.04,0:14:59.48,White,,0,0,0,,Mm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.76,0:15:36.72,White,,0,0,0,,(enrenou de converses)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.16,0:15:48.16,White,,0,0,0,,Porta esquerra, instal·lat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.04,0:15:52.64,White,,0,0,0,,Porta dreta, instal·lat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.40,0:15:55.40,White,,0,0,0,,Tot a punt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.48,0:15:58.36,White,,0,0,0,,Tres, dos, un..., endavant!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.24,0:16:10.24,White,,0,0,0,,(gent: cridòria)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.36,0:16:23.16,White,,0,0,0,,Som-hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.48,0:16:37.48,White,,0,0,0,,Eh? Però què...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.40,0:16:47.40,Yellow,,0,0,0,,L'esperàvem, senyor Zorro.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.56,0:16:54.80,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Em sap molt de greu, però aquesta nit se'ls ha acabat la festa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.88,0:16:57.32,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Som aquí perquè ja sabíem\Nque vindrien.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.60,0:16:59.60,White,,0,0,0,,-Si se sentien veus!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.60,0:16:59.60,White,,0,0,0,,-Com pot ser?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.68,0:17:01.12,White,,0,0,0,,Calleu tots dos.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.60,0:17:04.88,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Diu que... se sentien veus?\NAquestes, per exemple?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.96,0:17:07.04,White,,0,0,0,,(mòbil: enrenou de converses)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.64,0:17:17.64,White,,0,0,0,,O sigui que has sigut tu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.12,0:17:20.96,White,,0,0,0,,Ara me'n recordo.\NÉs el nen del penya-segat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.04,0:17:24.44,White,,0,0,0,,-Així, ell també és viu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.04,0:17:24.44,White,,0,0,0,,-Com és que encara és viu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.80,0:17:27.24,White,,0,0,0,,Em sap greu, noi,\Nperò no sé de què parles.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.32,0:17:29.32,White,,0,0,0,,Nosaltres només som especialistes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.40,0:17:32.52,White,,0,0,0,,Ens han contractat per fer\Nuna actuació a la festa d'avui.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.88,0:17:34.88,Yellow,,0,0,0,,No, no cal que dissimulin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.36,0:17:38.56,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ara ja pot sortir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.72,0:17:43.72,White,,0,0,0,,Ah..., ja m'ho pensava.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.80,0:17:47.44,White,,0,0,0,,Però si vam veure com queia!\NNo ho entenc! Què vol dir, això?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.84,0:17:52.76,White,,0,0,0,,D'acord, si el que vols és\Ntornar a morir...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.56,0:17:57.40,White,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.56,0:17:57.40,Green,,0,0,0,,Go Mizorogi, àlies el Zorro.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.40,0:18:01.12,Green,,0,0,0,,Queda detingut per robatori\Na mà armada i per homicidi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.64,0:18:04.36,White,,0,0,0,,I vosaltres dos també.\NNo cal que us hi resistiu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.56,0:18:24.76,White,,0,0,0,,Oh... D'acord.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.56,0:18:24.76,Green,,0,0,0,,Vinga, vostè també. Som-hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.64,0:18:31.12,White,,0,0,0,,Anem a confirmar-ho.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.64,0:18:31.12,Yellow,,0,0,0,,M'ho imaginava.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.48,0:18:33.20,White,,0,0,0,,Mm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.12,0:18:42.12,White,,0,0,0,,(telèfon: ring)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.44,0:18:46.56,Green,,0,0,0,,Inspector Megure, digui'm?\NHola, doctor Agasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.28,0:18:49.96,Green,,0,0,0,,Sí, sí, ja ho crec.\NAquesta vegada ha estat magnífic!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.40,0:18:52.80,Green,,0,0,0,,Què? Que hi ha més coses?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.80,0:18:58.24,White,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.56,0:19:01.60,White,,0,0,0,,-Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.56,0:19:01.60,White,,0,0,0,,-Ho tenia tot ben lligat, oi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.16,0:19:05.80,White,,0,0,0,,(veu Agasa) Que aquests de la foto\Nno són la seva dona i el seu fill.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.88,0:19:07.96,White,,0,0,0,,Va agafar aquesta fotografia\Nd'internet
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.04,0:19:10.76,White,,0,0,0,,i la va retocar per fer veure\Nque era la seva família.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.84,0:19:14.76,White,,0,0,0,,La va fer servir perquè el Zorro\Nes pensés que tenia un punt feble.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.84,0:19:17.00,White,,0,0,0,,Sabia que així confiaria més\Nen vostè.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.08,0:19:20.16,White,,0,0,0,,D'entrada, el que volia era\Nquedar-se tots els diners...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.24,0:19:22.24,White,,0,0,0,,que ell havia anat robant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.32,0:19:25.24,White,,0,0,0,,I quan va descobrir el número\Ni la contrasenya
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.32,0:19:27.12,White,,0,0,0,,del seu compte bancari secret,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.20,0:19:29.20,White,,0,0,0,,va decidir abandonar la banda\Ni llavors va actuar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.40,0:19:37.40,White,,0,0,0,,Mm... m'ho imaginava.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.48,0:19:40.40,White,,0,0,0,,Han començat a hackejar el sistema\Nde seguretat del seu pròxim objectiu
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.48,0:19:42.28,White,,0,0,0,,fent servir el meu programa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.96,0:19:44.40,Yellow,,0,0,0,,On tenen pensat atacar?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.04,0:19:48.16,White,,0,0,0,,Aaa... a la Sala d'Exposicions\Ndel barri de Beika.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.56,0:19:50.56,Yellow,,0,0,0,,D'acord.\NHem d'avisar la policia!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.24,0:20:02.24,White,,0,0,0,,(veu Agasa) En Conan i l'Ai\Nvan descobrir
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.32,0:20:04.32,White,,0,0,0,,que era la contrasenya\Nd'un compte estranger.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.40,0:20:06.88,White,,0,0,0,,Va traspassar tots els diners\Ndel compte del Zorro
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.96,0:20:09.12,White,,0,0,0,,a un altre compte a nom seu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.20,0:20:11.24,White,,0,0,0,,Ho va fer així\Nperquè va donar per fet
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.32,0:20:14.40,White,,0,0,0,,que vostè sortiria abans de la presó\Nque el Zorro.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.48,0:20:16.28,White,,0,0,0,,Tinc raó o no?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.68,0:20:18.48,White,,0,0,0,,Ah..., ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.24,0:20:22.48,Green,,0,0,0,,El felicito, doctor Agasa,\Naquesta vegada ha estat magistral.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.88,0:20:24.88,Green,,0,0,0,,Ens hem posat en contacte\Namb la Interpol
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.96,0:20:26.96,Green,,0,0,0,,i ja han congelat el compte.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.04,0:20:29.08,Green,,0,0,0,,Em sap molt de greu,\Nsenyor Isehara,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.16,0:20:31.16,Green,,0,0,0,,però ja no en podrà treure\Nni un ien.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.24,0:20:53.04,Songs,,0,0,0,,Kimi to nara\Nitsumade mo yume wo mite
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.40,0:20:59.16,Songs,,0,0,0,,aruite yukitai to negau.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.80,0:21:08.40,Songs,,0,0,0,,Nee tatoeba juunen mirai no
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.20,0:21:15.76,Songs,,0,0,0,,bokura wa dou shiteiru ka na.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.24,0:21:18.80,Songs,,0,0,0,,Yume no meiro nuke
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.92,0:21:21.24,Songs,,0,0,0,,doa no soto kimi ga ite
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.32,0:21:23.20,Songs,,0,0,0,,waratteru ka na.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.48,0:21:30.20,Songs,,0,0,0,,Kimi to nara\Nitsumade mo yume wo mite
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.64,0:21:36.08,Songs,,0,0,0,,aruite yukitai to negau.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.92,0:21:41.68,Songs,,0,0,0,,Ima mo boku wa yume no naka.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.04,0:21:48.96,Songs,,0,0,0,,Oikakete oikakete doko made mo
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.28,0:21:53.32,Songs,,0,0,0,,mada minu keshiki wo mezasu yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.40,0:21:55.60,Songs,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.80,0:22:02.04,Songs,,0,0,0,,Sore ga boku no yume\Nkimi to zutto.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.84,0:22:10.08,White,,0,0,0,,Diria que... no del tot.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.84,0:22:10.08,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Per fi s'ha acabat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.60,0:22:14.52,White,,0,0,0,,Tinguem la festa en pau, eh.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.60,0:22:14.52,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.08,0:22:18.28,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Aaa...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.08,0:22:18.28,White,,0,0,0,,(tots) No ens has de dir res?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.36,0:22:20.72,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Daixò..., perdoneu\Nper haver-vos fet patir.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.72,0:22:23.84,White,,0,0,0,,Vine aquí!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.72,0:22:23.84,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Em sap molt de greu!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.92,0:22:25.92,White,,0,0,0,,-Aquesta te la farem pagar!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.92,0:22:25.92,White,,0,0,0,,-No t'escaparàs.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.00,0:22:28.80,White,,0,0,0,,-No corris, vine aquí!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.00,0:22:28.80,White,,0,0,0,,-Ui, quan t'atrapi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.88,0:22:31.76,White,,0,0,0,,Ens pensàvem que eres mort!\NVine aquí!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.84,0:22:41.76,White,,0,0,0,,Hi ha un lloc on m'agradaria moltíssim anar, doctor Agasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.92,0:22:46.60,White,,0,0,0,,(tots) Som l'esquadró Origami,\Nels Nobuna Gaizers!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.72,0:22:51.08,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ah... Un espectacle de superherois.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.52,0:22:54.92,White,,0,0,0,,Suposo que s'han inspirat una mica\Nen en Nobunaga Oda.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.44,0:22:58.12,White,,0,0,0,,Els membres dels Nobuna Gaizers\Nsón...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.20,0:22:59.88,White,,0,0,0,,Eh? Aaaah...!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.52,0:23:02.52,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(veu Conan) No us perdeu\Nel pròxim episodi:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.60,0:23:05.12,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"El cas Nobunaga, 450è aniversari".
